section: bytecode
synopsis: Enable the bytecode interpreter to work with :ghc-flag:`-fhpc`.
issues: #27036
mrs: !15843

description: {
  Allows producing :ghc-flag:`-fhpc` information with the bytecode interpreter.

  We insert :ghc-flag:`-fhpc` ticks similar to how we insert :ghc-flag:`-fbreak-points` ticks.
  `hpc` is started, when the first byte code object with :ghc-flag:`-fhpc` information is loaded into
  the bytecode interpreter.
}
